 	<div id="main-article-info">
 		
					
				
			<h1
																									>Experience: I nearly died after eating wild mushrooms</h1>
				
					<p id="stand-first"
				 class="stand-first-alone"																				>'The scary thing about the Destroying Angel is that it tricks you into thinking you are making a recovery – then it destroys your liver'</p>
		
				
  	</div>
  	
  	  	<ul id="content-actions" class="share-links">
		                    
    
	
		
													

        
        
    <li class="share-links">
        <ul>
    
			
			
	
