                        <a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/society/2005/nov/10/health.lifeandhealth1?INTCMP=ILCNETTXT3487">Have I got ...</a>
                    </p>
                </li><li>
                    <p class="t6 web-publication-date">30 Sep 2005</p>
                    <p class="t7">
                        <a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2005/sep/30/ruralaffairs.foodanddrink?INTCMP=ILCNETTXT3487">What's good now?</a>
                    </p>
