				<h1>Experience: I nearly died after eating wild mushrooms</h1>
		   		    			    									   	This article appeared  on p14 of the <a href=http://www.guardian.co.uk/theguardian/2010/nov/13/weekend  >Weekend</a> section of 					   	<a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/theguardian"  >the Guardian</a>
					   	on <time datetime="2010-11-13" pubdate><a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/theguardian/2010/nov/13">Saturday 13 November 2010</a></time>.
					   	It was published on
							<a href='http://www.guardian.co.uk/'>guardian.co.uk</a>
							at <time datetime="2010-11-13T00:00GMT" pubdate>00.02 GMT on Saturday 13 November 2010</time>.
					   	
