							<p>Ouch, kindof puts my experience when a kid into a new light.</p><p>I didn't know much about mushrooms, but when I found one in a field and was hungry I just ate it...all I remember is that it was white, tasty and musty and looked a lot like the ones in the shops.</p><p>I think I was one rather lucky 10yr old.</p><p>It did nothing to me, but my mum was rather anoyed at me...I just thought she was being over the top...as you do when you are 10.</p>
						
