<img class="author-profile-picture" src="http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/discussion/avatars/2010/09/06/maxsceptic1/3474b3ce-cd3d-4d9f-863d-fcbcf31a5162/60x60.png" height="60" width="60" alt="" />
<a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/discussion/user/maxsceptic1" title="User profile page">maxsceptic1</a>

                            
